intermediate results from data-owners. Our protocol\nis also provably safe (sharing the same safety as the homomorphic encryption\nschemes), differently from other techniques such as\nOrder-Preserving/Revealing-Encryption (OPE/ORE).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 29 Oct 2018 19:44:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 9 May 2019 19:02:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-05-13"}
