icle. Hence, the use of the dual system of\nevaluation for reducing costs might introduce unknown biases in a research\nassessment exercise.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 29 Oct 2018 22:06:43 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 17 Oct 2019 06:38:48 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 1 Apr 2020 14:32:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-12-15"}
