erconductivity since the screening of the\nelectric field is efficient in such materials, suppressing the internal\nelectric field too weak to occur superconductivity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 30 Oct 2018 03:12:27 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 31 Jul 2019 22:40:33 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 2 Oct 2019 02:13:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-03"}
