utonomous flights in a 3D wind tunnel. Using this data,\naerodynamic model selection, parameter identification, and discrimination\nbetween aerodynamic and contact forces could be done. Finally, the developed\nmethods could serve as useful estimators for interaction control schemes with\nsimultaneous compensation of wind disturbances.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 30 Oct 2018 10:32:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-11-01"}
